# Motion, A11y & Performance

- Use Framer Motion only where needed; respect `prefers-reduced-motion` (reduce or disable non-essential motion).
- Semantic HTML (section, nav, main, header, footer). Visible keyboard focus states; aria-label/aria-labelledby on interactive controls.
- Prefer server components; use client components only for interactivity or motion. Optimize images and animation cost; no unnecessary libraries.
